snippet.title: Love Is Gone - SLANDER, Dylan Matthew (Cover by 宇洋鐘, Amber Wu, Ray)
snippet.description:
We have started this cover series during Taiwan Covid-19 level 3 restrictions, hoping  that not only our country, but entire world can make through this hard time as soon as possible.

Original Song : Love Is Gone - SLANDER, Dylan Matthew

Singer : 宇洋鐘, Amber Wu, Ray
Piano : Ray
Beat Making : Mr. HUANG
Mixing & Mastering : Mr. HUANG
Image design : Way-Jay Chou
